            <title>[LUDOC-533] Current intended level of support for Linux (user) namespaces</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-533</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;What is Lustre&apos;s current level of support for Linux namespaces?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have been using namespaces on an HPC system, an have recently run into some issues. I have not been able to find any information on this other than the issue tracker showing some changes for conforming to kernel APIs, so it isn&apos;t clear to me if any issues I run into are bugs, or that there just hasn&apos;t been any work to support things yet.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
